            <li><strong>Reassure</strong> — tell them they did the right thing, it's not their fault</li>
            <li><strong>Be honest</strong> — explain you will need to tell someone who can help</li>
            <li><strong>Record accurately</strong> — write the child's exact words as soon as possible</li>
            <li><strong>Report immediately</strong> — contact the DSL the same day</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
